         <abstract id="aspace_b931c21e868bb59ff623889fabd956ff">Thecollection contains: two manuscripts of carols, a single "Noel- Nouveau" and a collection of carols by Raymondus, Curio Parochiae St. Stephani as well as two letters regarding Reed's collection and a notebook Reed kept on his research on the history of carols.</abstract>
