      <scopecontent id="aspace_b53feccbfadf981889d701cd46964950">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The Edward Bliss Reed Carol Collection brings together the manuscript portion of items collected by Edward Bliss Reed. The Yale library system has various other printed items about carols given by Mr. Reed. These have been cataloged separately.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
